snippet.title: Jack Jeanne - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Kisa is about to give up her dream of being an actor when she is given the chance to go to the prestigious All Boys Drama School with 2 conditions. 
Will Kisa be able to compete against her classmates and win the lead role in the final performance? and keep her identity a secret?

JackJeanne comes to Nintendo Switch 2023!

https://www.aksysgames.com/jackjeanne/
